---
@META
dir: skillsPraut/scripts/
updated: 2026-04-13
files: 2
stack: Node.js (ESM), Bash

@EXPORTS
extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs: CLI script — extracts icon glyphs from Phosphor CSS to JSON
install-skill.sh: CLI script — symlinks skill into ~/.claude/skills/remotion

@FUNCTIONS
extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs() → void
  purpose: parse style.css → phosphor-glyphs.json
  side-effects: file (writes src/components/icons/phosphor-glyphs.json)

install-skill.sh() → void
  purpose: symlink skills/remotion to ~/.claude/skills/remotion
  side-effects: file (creates symlink)

@PROCESSES
glyph-extraction: phosphor-icons/Fonts/regular/style.css → regex .ph-<name>:before → JSON → phosphor-glyphs.json
skill-install: detect existing → mkdir -p → ln -s → confirm

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: phosphor-icons/Fonts/regular/style.css (input for glyphs)
external: node:fs | node:path | node:url

@STANDARDS
- Run glyphs via: npm run extract-glyphs
- install-skill.sh: idempotent — detects existing symlink
- Exits with code 1 if no glyphs extracted or dir exists (not symlink)
---
